org.osate.aadl2

Interface Property

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AbstractNamedValue, AObject, ArraySizeProperty, BasicProperty, Element, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.core.runtime.IAdaptable, NamedElement, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, TypedElement
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    PropertyImpl

    public interface Property
extends BasicProperty, AbstractNamedValue, ArraySizeProperty
    A representation of the model object 'Property Definition'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Inherit
    • Default Value
    • Applies To Metaclass
    • Applies To Classifier
    • Applies To
    • Empty List Default

    See Also:
    Aadl2Package.getProperty()
